events.name: Rod Stewart
events.description: The Rod Stewart event at Footprint Center, originally scheduled for Friday, June 24, 2022 has been postponed and will now take place on Friday, August 4, 2023. Tickets from the original date will be honored for this new date, however, we understand circumstances may have changed.

Presale will be available Thursday, January 26 from 10am-10pm. Tickets go on sale to the public on Friday, January 27 at 10am local.
